{"tid":1478614,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[818維園集會 中共劇本]","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T14:41:32.000Z","uid":68822,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8cacd5679cfd482609c6d9aeee625675c37a1ca7","tid":1478614,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"事源：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【求FC】 入境處同海關巴絲，我求下你地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1478014/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1478014/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n入境Fact Checked 有大批大陸仔帶齊gear落黎香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1478422/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1478422/page/1</a><br />\n</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n如根據以上既巴絲而言<br />\n中共派大量年青人扮黑衣勇武示威者<br />\n可能會喺818集會以外嘅地方大肆破壞各地警處、政府地方、堵塞馬路、進行各種破壞<br />\n因為818集會中有大量外國傳媒直播報道<br />\n中共一定唔敢向和平集會嘅市民落手<br />\n維園以外嘅地方警力同平民將會減少<br />\n搵果班黑蝗蟲落黎扮示威者進行對抗/傷害/甚至殺害都未定<br />\n扮演一場警民衝突再搵人拍片影相<br />\n完美抹黑真正嘅香港市民 從而令香港失去或減低國際支持<br />\n抹黑示威者形象 然而動用輿論文宣等喺各國論壇大肆抹黑<br />\n網上唔少傳言中共將會搵人際旗殺害<br />\n對無所不用其極嘅中共完全唔出其<br />\n喺維穩方面中共喺經濟上絕對能收買外國KOL喺佢地社交平台抹黑<br />\n喺818做一場警共合作SHOW比全球睇<br />\n<br />\n以上純熟9up"},{"pid":"04d85a96a23cea9f74fea9fa171fd96cf2cee1e1","tid":1478614,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"老掉牙"},{"pid":"02342bba1b2f33ead06a05b9b6ba0e011c4f95ae","tid":1478614,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04d85a96a23cea9f74fea9fa171fd96cf2cee1e1","tid":1478614,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"老掉牙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467def3fc0ae69f4489a9a657f18eeb4e8214c91","tid":1478614,"uid":27416